query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('aem',
'draw',
'drupal-6',
'jsf-2.2',
'lotus-domino',
'mamp',
'nstimer',
'pyinstaller',
'sympy',
'typeclass',
'x509certificate');
